languages.text: "Конечно я понимаю, что мое благосостояние не сравнится с вашим, шерин, и деньгами вас не удивить. Но я также могу предложить нечто иное — свои безграничные знания! Уверена, вы оцените услуги специалиста по ведению торговых дел. Там, откуда я родом, такую сделку называют "продажей мудрости".

traits.locale_text: "Уверена, мое благосостояние не сравнится с вашим, шерин, и деньгами я вас не заинтересую. Однако могу предложить вам нечто иное — свои безграничные знания! Уверена, вы оцените услуги специалиста по ведению торговых дел. Там, откуда я родом, такую сделку называют "продажей мудрости".

languages.text: "Of course, I am aware that my personal means cannot compare to yours, shereen, so I do not hope to impress you with money. But I can offer something else — my boundless knowledge! Surely you will appreciate the services of an expert on trading operations. Where I'm from, they call this kind of deal 'wisdom selling.'"

languages.text: 「もちろんあたし個人の資金力はアンタの足元にも及ばないだろうから、金銭でアピールすることはできないよ、シャリーン。でも、無限の知識なら与えられる！貿易業務の専門家の助言は何かと役に立つと思う。あたしの出身地では、こういった取引を『知恵の売買』と呼んでいるんだ」
languages.original_text: "Of course, I am aware that my personal means cannot compare to yours, shereen, so I do not hope to impress you with money. But I can offer something else — my boundless knowledge! Surely you will appreciate the services of an expert on trading operations. Where I'm from, they call this kind of deal 'wisdom selling.'"

languages.text: “自然，我很清楚我的财力远不如你，亲爱的，因此恐怕我没办法通过金钱来提供满意的报酬。不过，我还可以为你提供其他东西，比如说——我无穷无尽的知识！我这位贸易专家提供的贴心服务，保证会让你满意。在我的家乡，人们把这称为‘智识交易’。”
languages.original_text: "Of course, I am aware that my personal means cannot compare to yours, shereen, so I do not hope to impress you with money. But I can offer something else — my boundless knowledge! Surely you will appreciate the services of an expert on trading operations. Where I'm from, they call this kind of deal 'wisdom selling.'"

traits.locale_text: “我很清楚我的财力自然比不上你，亲爱的，因此我不会以金钱作为报答。不过，我还可以为你提供其他东西，例如——我无穷无尽的知识！我这位贸易专家提供的贴心服务，保证会让你满意。在我的家乡，人们把这称为‘智识交易’。”

languages.text: « Bien sûr, mes maigres moyens ne sont rien par rapport aux vôtres, shereen. Je ne peux donc espérer vous impressionner avec mes finances. En revanche, je peux vous offrir autre chose : mon savoir illimité ! À n'en pas douter, vous apprécierez les services d'une experte en matière commerciale. D'où je viens, on nomme ce genre d'accord une "transaction expérientielle". »
languages.original_text: "Of course, I am aware that my personal means cannot compare to yours, shereen, so I do not hope to impress you with money. But I can offer something else — my boundless knowledge! Surely you will appreciate the services of an expert on trading operations. Where I'm from, they call this kind of deal 'wisdom selling.'"

traits.locale_text: « Je suis sûre que mes maigres moyens ne sont rien par rapport aux vôtres, shereen. Je ne peux donc pas vous proposer un dédommagement financier. Je peux cependant vous offrir autre chose : mon savoir illimité ! À n'en pas douter, vous apprécierez les services d'une experte en matière commerciale. D'où je viens, on nomme ce genre d'accord une ‘transaction expérientielle'. »

languages.text: «Por supuesto, sé que mis recursos tienen mucho que envidiar a los suyos, shereen; no puede interesarle mi fortuna. Eso sí, puedo ofrecerle algo más: ¡mi conocimiento ilimitado! Seguro que le vendrían bien los servicios de una experta en operaciones comerciales. En mi barrio a ese tipo de transacciones lo llamamos "venta de sabiduría"».
languages.original_text: "Of course, I am aware that my personal means cannot compare to yours, shereen, so I do not hope to impress you with money. But I can offer something else — my boundless knowledge! Surely you will appreciate the services of an expert on trading operations. Where I'm from, they call this kind of deal 'wisdom selling.'"

traits.locale_text: «Estoy convencida de que mis propios medios tienen mucho que envidiar a los suyos, shereen; no puede interesarle mi fortuna. Puedo, eso sí, ofrecerle algo más: ¡mi conocimiento ilimitado! Seguro que le vendrían bien los servicios de una experta en operaciones comerciales. En mi barrio a ese tipo de transacciones lo llamamos "venta de sabiduría"».

languages.text: "Mir ist natürlich bewusst, dass sich meine persönlichen Mittel mit den Euren nicht messen können, Shereen. Mit meinem Geld werde ich Euch also wohl kaum beeindrucken. Allerdings kann ich Euch etwas anderes bieten ... mein grenzenloses Wissen! Ihr wisst die Dienste einer Expertin für Handelsoperationen doch sicher zu schätzen. Wo ich herkomme, bezeichnet man solche Geschäfte als 'Verkauf von Weisheit'."
languages.original_text: "Of course, I am aware that my personal means cannot compare to yours, shereen, so I do not hope to impress you with money. But I can offer something else — my boundless knowledge! Surely you will appreciate the services of an expert on trading operations. Where I'm from, they call this kind of deal 'wisdom selling.'"

traits.locale_text: "Ich bin sicher, meine persönlichen Mittel können sich mit den Euren nicht messen. Ich kann Euch also wohl kaum mit Geld locken. Allerdings kann ich etwas anderes anbieten ... mein grenzenloses Wissen! Ihr wisst die Dienste einer Expertin für Handelsoperationen doch sicher zu schätzen. Wo ich herkomme, bezeichnet man solche Geschäfte als "Verkauf von Weisheit".

languages.original_text: "Of course, I am aware that my personal means cannot compare to yours, shereen, so I do not hope to impress you with money. But I can offer something else — my boundless knowledge! Surely you will appreciate the services of an expert on trading operations. Where I'm from, they call this kind of deal 'wisdom selling.'"

languages.text: "Tabii benim şahsi imkânlarımla seninkiler denk değil, farkındayım şirinim. Bu yüzden de seni parayla etkilemeyi ümit edemem. Lakin bambaşka bir şey teklif edebilirim: Engin irfanımı! Ticari işlemler uzmanı olarak sunabileceğim hizmetlerden memnun kalacağından eminim. Bizim oralarda bu işe 'akıl satmak' denir."

traits.locale_text: "Tabii benim şahsi imkanlarımla seninkiler denk değil, onun farkındayım şirinim. Bu yüzden de seni parayla etkilemeye yönelik bir umudum yok. Asıl teklif ettiğimse bambaşka... Engin irfanım! Ticari işlemlerin eksperi olarak sunabileceğim hizmetlerden memnun kalacağından eminim. Bizim oralarda bu işe 'akıl satmak' denir."
